de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mkcop

Class MkCoPDirectoryEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.AbstractDirectoryEntry
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.MTreeDirectoryEntry
        • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mkcop.MkCoPDirectoryEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DirectoryEntry, Entry, MkCoPEntry, MTreeEntry, Externalizable, Serializable

     class MkCoPDirectoryEntry
extends MTreeDirectoryEntry
implements MkCoPEntry
    Represents an entry in a directory node of an MkCop-Tree. Additionally to an MTreeDirectoryEntry an MkCoPLeafEntry holds the conservative approximation of its knn-distances.
    Since:
    0.2
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
